      "instruction": "<p>While the aubergine and sweet potato are in the oven, peel and finely chop your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Roughly chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong></p><p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and roughly chop</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-15-1702989454619-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
