            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a pot with a little drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped tomato</strong>, <strong>pepper</strong> and<strong> garlic</strong> with <strong>half</strong> your <strong>oregano </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until beginning to soften</p><p>Meanwhile, grate your <strong>cheddar</strong> <strong>cheese </strong>finely</p><p>Wash your<strong> spinach</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-19-1702989459516-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-19-1702989459516-x400.jpg",
