            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once slightly softened, add your<strong> tomato paste</strong> with 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[140ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[180ml]</span><strong> boiled water</strong> and your <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until slightly thickened</p><p>Once thickened, blitz with a <strong>(stick) blender </strong>until smooth –<strong> </strong>this is your <strong>tomato & pepper sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-14-1702989465395-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
