            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sauce has thickened, some of the <strong>cooked aubergine slices</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> in a single layer</p><p>Spoon over some of the <strong>tomato & pepper sauce</strong>, then add a layer of <strong>spinach</strong></p><p>Layer on the <strong>sweet potato slices</strong>, then repeat the process with the <strong>remaining aubergine </strong>– this is your <strong>parmigiana</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
