    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the <strong>roasted aubergine & sweet potato parmigiana</strong> has cooked, allow it to cool slightly before serving (this helps the flavours to develop and makes it easier to serve!)</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining basil leaves</strong> and a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
